# AI Website Summary

- **Route**: `GET /summary?url=<url>`.
- **Response**: `{ title, summary }`. Uses Workers AI to summarize body text.
- **Bindings**: `[ai]` binding = "AI". Model in constants (e.g. llama-3.1-8b-instruct).
